    "title": "WebCatalog: Turn Websites into Desktop Apps for Seamless Productivity",
    "excerpt": "Discover how WebCatalog transforms any website into a desktop app, letting you manage multiple accounts and workspaces effortlessly. Try it today!",
    "featured_image": {
      "$media": {
        "url": "https://tonyciencia.com/blog/why-choose-webcatalog.jpg",
