    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Why Choose WebCatalog for Your Productivity?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://try.webcatalog.io/h8kuam5b12qt"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you're tired of juggling browser tabs for different accounts or web apps, WebCatalog is here to simplify everything. This tool converts any website into a native desktop app, letting you manage multiple accounts, organize workspaces by workflow, and access everything from one unified place. I've been using it for months, and the boost in my daily workflow is incredible—no more clutter or switching between browsers. For anyone looking to streamline their digital life, ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "explore WebCatalog now",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and see the difference.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Key Features That Make WebCatalog Stand Out",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "WebCatalog isn't just another app; it's a productivity powerhouse. You can create desktop apps for sites like Gmail, Trello, or social media platforms, each with its own isolated session. This means no more logging in and out when handling multiple client accounts. The workspace organization feature lets you group apps by projects—imagine having a \"Marketing\" workspace with all your tools in one window. Plus, the curated catalog offers ready-made apps, saving you setup time. It's all about making your digital environment as efficient as possible.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "New and Highlighted Features to Love",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/webcatalog-new-features"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Recently, WebCatalog has rolled out enhancements that take it further. The improved interface now supports better customization, like assigning icons and names to your apps for quick recognition. There's also enhanced support for web apps that require complex logins, ensuring seamless operation. These updates, detailed in ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "WebCatalog's new features",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", show the team's commitment to user feedback and innovation. It keeps getting better, making it a tool you'll want to stay with long-term.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Who Is WebCatalog Ideal For?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-clickup"
          },
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-monday-com"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "WebCatalog is perfect for anyone who relies on web-based tools but craves desktop efficiency. Remote workers managing multiple clients, freelancers switching between platforms like Upwork and Slack, or students organizing study apps—everyone benefits. If you use tools like ClickUp or monday.com, WebCatalog integrates smoothly; for example, you can create a dedicated app for ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "how to use ClickUp",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " or ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "monday.com",
            "marks": [
              "l3"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " to keep work separate from personal browsing. It's designed for those who value speed, organization, and a clutter-free workflow.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Real-World Use Cases to Inspire You",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
