            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Let me share how I use it daily: as a content creator, I have separate apps for my blogging platform, social media schedulers, and analytics dashboards—all accessible without opening a browser. This setup cuts down my loading times and distractions. For business teams, it's a game-changer; imagine having Apollo.io as a standalone app for prospecting—check out ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "how to use Apollo.io",
            "marks": [
              "l4"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " for tips. The possibilities are endless, from personal productivity to collaborative projects, and you can dive deeper into ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "use cases",
            "marks": [
              "l5"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
