          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Getting started is straightforward: download WebCatalog, add your favorite websites, and customize your workspaces. The ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "step-by-step tutorial",
            "marks": [
              "l6"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " guides you through every detail, from creating apps to organizing them. I recommend starting with a few key sites you use daily—like your email or project manager—to feel the immediate benefits. It's free to try, and once you see the time you save, you'll wonder how you ever managed without it. Ready to transform your workflow? ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Try WebCatalog for yourself",
            "marks": [
              "l7"
